  Change: 48fe96111bc7b4130989bcbaa5e9c15447b3fd3f
  Author: Alceu Rodrigues de Freitas Junior <arfreitas@cpan.org>
  Date : 2017-05-26 22:01:15 +0000

    Moving Syscalls.pm generation outside Makefile.PL

    Generating the code from Makefile.PL is generating problems when
    Inline dependency is not yet installed Created build_my_module.PL to
    generate the module AFTER the Makefile.PL is executed, during "make"
    execution Still need to figure out how to make build_my_module.PL to
    be executed before the Syscalls.pm is copied from lib to blib 

